  (text "KEY MATRIX  5x12 (59 keys, COL2ROW diodes)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "667bc305-08e4-540e-9f99-ec2d5ee98f03"))
  (text "MCU -- RP2040 (VERIFY pin numbers before fab, see file header)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "3bb58a63-4058-578c-8672-292df556bbb8"))
  (text "RP2040 minimum system (core regulator, 12MHz xtal, QSPI flash)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 63.5 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "9b7bc714-2962-5668-aa5f-e64c0b0b0792"))
  (text "Wireless (CYW43439, BLE-only) -- crystal/pinout/power topology verified against datasheet 002-30348 Rev *D; RF matching values still VERIFY (vendor/antenna-specific)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 114.3 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "33145fe3-6413-5aa0-bc26-70b0739cde7b"))
  (text "Per-key RGB -- SK6812MINI-E x59, serpentine chain (must match Sources/smk/RGBLighting.swift ledChainIndex)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 45.72 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "f2c893f7-3ecd-5695-9918-c0cd0ef2f506"))
  (text "RGB power budget (calculated from the SK6812MINI-E datasheet, 12mA/channel x 3 x 59 LEDs = 2.12A max at full white): fed from VSYS, NOT the 3.3V LDO (AP2112K-3.3 isn't remotely rated for this). D60 (B5819W, ~1A avg rating) IS in this path when USB-powered and WOULD be exceeded by 2.12A -- firmware must cap brightness/concurrent-on count well below full-white-all-keys regardless of power source. Also VERIFY: SK6812MINI-E's own datasheet specs VDD 3.7-5.5V, and VSYS (Li-ion battery) can sag below 3.7V well within normal discharge range -- LEDs may misbehave on a low battery even with brightness capped. Level shifter keeps DIN threshold margin safe across the VSYS voltage range (separate from the VDD-minimum concern above)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 38.1 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "ab8f448f-41d7-537d-bd7d-60ab2984504e"))
  (text "USB-C  (charge + native USB)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 219.71 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "26a7a0d4-ee15-59b6-820b-356d84271371"))
  (text "Li-ion charger 500mA" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 287.02 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "d978fac2-8dde-5cdc-b5ac-ac4bc75bb54f"))
  (text "Power path + 3.3V LDO + ON/OFF" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 340.36 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "c28553a9-00a3-55b1-b7ed-3231b6ac1034"))
  (text "VBAT sense + RESET + BOOTSEL" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 391.16 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "1b6bec94-30f9-5dff-a0d2-3af0984b9c1a"))
  (text "GPIO map (VERIFY pin numbers, see file header):  ROW0-4 = GPIO0-4   COL0-11 = GPIO5-16   RGB_GPIO = GPIO17   VBAT_SENSE = GPIO26/ADC0   BT UART/ctrl (GPIO18-23, 28) = CYW43439 BLE link (see wireless section)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 95.25 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "4dbaff86-505c-519c-b025-8ec81cbdc2a6"))
  (text "Charging works with power switch OFF (charger connects before switch).  BOOTSEL+RESET = USB mass-storage bootloader mode (VERIFY)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "ff5d50a0-237b-5442-ab64-dad32714c10f"))
